'''靜蟹科'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''Galenidae'''}}）是[[短尾下目|短尾下目]][[毛刺蟹總科|毛刺蟹總科]]的三個科當中的第二大，包括有四個由各自的屬組成的亞科<ref name="Ng">{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2008 |volume=17 |pages=1–286 |title=Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant Brachyuran crabs of the world |author=Peter K. L. Ng, Danièle Guinot & Peter J. F. Davie |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |access-date=2014-03-13 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606061453/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2009 |volume=Suppl. 21 |pages=1–109 |title=A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |author=Sammy De Grave, N. Dean Pentcheff, Shane T. Ahyong ''et al.'' |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |access-date=2014-03-13 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==簡述==
本科包含了原來的[[長腳蟹科|長腳蟹科]]及[[扇蟹科|扇蟹科]]之下的幾個非典型屬，所以其外貌跟其他毛刺蟹總科不大相同，其甲殼並沒有很明顯的「毛刺」<ref name="Ng" />。

==分類==
靜蟹科包括以下四個亞科<ref name="Ng" /><ref name="Grave" />：
*[[Denthoxanthinae|Denthoxanthinae]] <small>Števčić, 2005</small>
** ''[[Dentoxanthus|Dentoxanthus]]'' <small>Stephensen, 1946</small> 
*[[靜蟹亞科|靜蟹亞科]] Galeninae <small>Alcock, 1898</small>
** [[靜蟹屬|靜蟹屬]] ''Galene'' <small>De Haan, 1833</small><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wetland.org.tw/trip/class/crab/word-1.htm |title=台南市螃蟹名錄 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2014-03-13 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305034727/http://www.wetland.org.tw/trip/class/crab/word-1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*[[暴蟹亞科|暴蟹亞科]] Halimedinae <small>Alcock, 1898</small>
** [[暴蟹屬|暴蟹屬]] ''Halimede'' <small>De Haan, 1835</small> 
*[[Parapanopinae|Parapanopinae]] <small>Števčić, 2005</small>
** ''[[Parapanope|Parapanope]]'' <small>De Man, 1895</small>

